t TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE\n);\n\nCREATE INDEX idx_chats_project ON chat_sessions(project_id);\n```\n\n**TUI Deprecation Path**:\n- TUI continues to work with its own legacy session storage\n- No migration needed - web starts fresh\n- Eventually remove TUI entirely\n\n**Does this web-first, project-required approach work for you?**\n\n---\n\nIf yes, I'll proceed to the final design section (Error Handling & Edge Cases) and then write the complete spec document.",
